A GWA calculator made specifically for project based learning

#System flow

The user starts by entering the amount of their *subjects*, proceedingly subjects and grades would be stored in an
array - size of the array would be initiallized based from the first input.

Next part onto another class two methods will be created. **to put it simply the methods of this class aims to convert
the grades into a grade point**

Proceeding to the next class inherited form the very first class, the method from this class tends to do all
of the computations necessary to produce the desired output.